íŸ@2d5ea101dbb5d67a39eb23fd08f9cca39cda8cc78e52d021c2f909491f81397f⁄ÆTitle: title: if
Path: Examples
Content:
Output a value if a condition matches, otherwise return nothing.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> if 2 < 3 { 'yes!' }
yes!

```
Output a value if a condition matches, else return another value.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> if 5 < 3 { 'yes!' } else { 'no!' }
no!

```
Chain multiple if's together.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> if 5 < 3 { 'yes!' } else if 4 < 5 { 'no!' } else { 'okay!' }
no!

```
